A group of Boston investors andinvestment partnerships told the Securities and ExchangeCommission it sold its entire stake in Silicon Systems Inc of410,000 shares, or 6.0 pct of the total outstanding.    The group, which includes HLM Associates, HLM Associates IIand their three general partners, said it sold the stockbetween April 22 and June 9 at 9.00 to 9.125 dlrs a share asthe result of an investment decision. Reuter&#3;